,  ""       South park: the fractured but whole DansGame
We are currently playing on version 1.9.8. We would like to know why some features or convenient mechanics were cut in the new version 2.0 beta?
Hello there! Streamer asked why have you removed a lot of content from the newest version?

The reason i removed almost everything in the new update was for a lot of reasons. 1- I saw that the community didn't really like the difficulty, some levels and bosses designs 2- A lot of content was scrapped or cutted 3- Almost the 50% of bosses and levels were directly copied from other fangames. So now i wanted to make everything on my own and style 4- And lastly, to add much more content than before
5 : 1. drug_solo - 39 pts 2. rng_guy - 30 pts 3. cahmek - 26 pts 4. maxim11l1anchik - 22 pts 5. jokere98 - 18 pts
